'''Azunmenẓaw n Lhend''' (S [[Tutlayt tahendayt|Thendayt]]: भारतीय उपमहाद्वीप), (S [[Tutlayt Urdu|Urdu]]: برصغير) d amur n wakan meqqren deg [[amenẓaw|umenẓaw]] n [[Asya]] tettawi timura yellan deg [[Tafilt tatektunt]] n Lhend am: [[Bingladic]], [[Pakistan]], [[Lhend]], [[Butan]], [[Nipal]] akk d [[tigzirt (tasnamurt)|tegzirin]] id yezzin am [[Sri Lanka]] d [[Maldiv]].

== Tama tasnamurt ==
Azunmenzaw n Lhend d akal id yezgan si tama n wadda n [[idurar n Himalaya]] akk d [[agni n Tibit]], Deg tama n uneẓẓul yezzi-yas-d [[Agaraw amelwi|ugaraw amelwi]], Seg umalu [[ilel aɛrab]].

== Imezdaɣ ==
Azal n 1,700,000,000 n ifganen ttidiren deg azunmenẓaw n Lhend, gar-asen ugar n 65% ttidiren deg [[Lhend]], Ttmeslayen aṭas n [[Tutlayt|tutlayin]] (ugar n 1000).
